{"tid":604787,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"派110億料明年初申請　陳茂波指行政費只佔幾個%","createTime":"2018-03-25T05:28:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T06:44:36.000Z","uid":127988,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3012f090bdc9cb695339de35b83c7462ec715aab","tid":604787,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:28:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180325/57992032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F57992032&d=rnLJWTJRiABdN9x9mvKqbxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=aaa8a170\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F57992032&h=06cb4233\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180325/57992032</a><br />\n<br />\n政府前日宣佈以補漏拾遺方式向合資格人士派發4,000元，亦會向獲退稅、免差餉，但金額不足4,000元人士派發差額。政府預計合資格市民約有280萬人，涉及約110億，被質疑派錢方式複雜，行政費極高。財政司長陳茂波今發表網誌表示，初步估計派錢成本比率為總金額的「數個百分點」，並爭取明年2月或之前開始接受市民申請。如以110億元派發金額計算，如行政費為5%，即5.5億元。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波以〈關愛共享計劃〉為題，撰文表示有關派錢計劃可讓「用心照顧家庭而未能工作的婦女、剛退休而沒有領取津貼的『年輕長者』，以及收入不高、沒有交稅的人士，以至其他年齡層的打工仔」受惠。他又指因升學或工作等原因暫時離開香港，或新來港定居人士，亦符合資格。<br />\n<br />\n陳指由於派錢工作非政府恆常工作，故需額外辦公空間及增聘人手等，計劃行政成本取決於實際申請人數，初步估計成本佔整個派錢金額數個百分點，又表示會盡最大努力減低相關開支。<br />\n根據2011年政府宣佈向全民派發6,000元，涉金額380億元，總行政費達2億。參考關愛基金於2016年推出「N無津貼」的行政費，每宗申請平均需143元，<span style=\"color: red;\">今次派錢料達4億，與陳茂波表示的全額中幾個%相若。 </span> <br />\n<br />\n天才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19681071e3a78911ec686d39180f28a47cc76eb","tid":604787,"uid":810,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:31:07.000Z","msg":"偷換概念<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n本身個5.5億唔洗浪費<br />\n波叔係咪老人痴呆"},{"pid":"1ddaab7aa18501658ae9dc14a69e7bd66fe9784b","tid":604787,"uid":127988,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:31:15.000Z","msg":"曾俊華於2011年宣佈向全港永久性居民派發6,000元，當年整個計劃花費達380億元，立法會資料顯示，支付給銀行、香港郵政的手續費及宣傳等費用合計達1.3億元，政府亦額外撥款7,580萬元增聘人手，<span style=\"color: red;\">總行政費用逾2億元，佔整體費用的0.53%。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180324/57988163\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57988163&d=rnLJWTJRiABdN9x9mvKqbxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=09aba224\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180324%2F57988163&h=0887ffd6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180324/57988163</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人地派錢成本1%都唔夠, 阿茂波點解可以幾個%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98aaa7fb62e3f0529dd164c23913115b659b5cb0","tid":604787,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"奴才係聽話就架 唔需要識計數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e93b2c62a3571443ce7ef913b47c43f259291fc","tid":604787,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:35:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4fe74486b8377b6e268c141c601772b9e2c0a6","tid":604787,"uid":127988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T05:43:37.000Z","msg":"每宗申請平均需143元，今次派錢料達4億，與陳茂波表示的全額中幾個%相若。 (2018)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府會與 銀行簽訂服務合約，而銀行會就<br />\n每宗成功登記個案 (經電子銀行登記的除外)向政府收取 15 元，以收回<br />\n為計劃提供服務所需的行政費用。(2011)<br />\n<br />\n阿茂波真係計數勁過品客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7141d1834634e6e5